{"tid":2318241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你叫我罷買我偏要買","createTime":"2020-12-09T07:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T09:34:25.000Z","uid":219564,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"045a2f350558bbe39bf6f23fab75186d8bb19c66","tid":2318241,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"深受拉丁裔美國人喜愛的戈雅食品（Goya Foods）的第三代繼人、首席執行官羅伯特‧烏納努埃（Robert Unanue）日前在白宮出席活動時，對特朗普讚嘆不矣，他說：「我們有像特朗普這樣的總統，真的非常幸運，特朗普是一位建設者！」<br />\n<br />\n結果令公司隨即在網上慘遭評擊，且抵制該產品之聲不絕。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">左膠AOC係咁叫人抵制呢間公司，點知人哋sales 上升咗 1000%，仲要係德州生產多一倍嘅貨。<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日間公司個CEO話AOC係佢地嘅 employee of the month<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CIkWPjZDQ8o/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCIkWPjZDQ8o%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=6213fe41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCIkWPjZDQ8o%2F&h=4cd08dcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CIkWPjZDQ8o/</a>"},{"pid":"8d49924d5eff0a76da5fcf74f13183b4e44bc0c5","tid":2318241,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9bd02bc158756225a6cd782d41ceb22263df4a","tid":2318241,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c6c0275b1e4a621bd5da10819e27a012e31ad1","tid":2318241,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:34:25.000Z","msg":"香港左膠都有咁嘅號召力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}